      <title>Hexo+Github搭建网站系列：基础教程（二）</title>
      <link href="/posts/990b/"/>
      <url>/posts/990b/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/08/pSVzWfU.png" alt="image-20221215222537719"></p><h4 id="原作者：crystal-修改者：墨晓"><a href="#原作者：crystal-修改者：墨晓" class="headerlink" title="原作者：crystal 修改者：墨晓"></a>原作者：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60578464">crystal</a> 修改者：<a href="https://www.kwink.ml/posts/7775/">墨晓</a></h4><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>本篇主要来点稍微高级的域名配置</p><h2 id="1-绑定域名（可选，还是有为好）"><a href="#1-绑定域名（可选，还是有为好）" class="headerlink" title="1.绑定域名（可选，还是有为好）"></a>1.绑定域名（可选，还是有为好）</h2><h4 id="1-1前提准备"><a href="#1-1前提准备" class="headerlink" title="1.1前提准备"></a>1.1前提准备</h4><ul><li><a href="https://iyideng.net/welfare/freenom-free-domain-register.html#:~:text=2%E3%80%81%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%20Freenom%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%201%20%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%20%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%9C%A8%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E2%80%9C%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%80%A7%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC%E5%88%B0%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E5%B0%B1%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84IP%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E2%80%9C%20%E6%98%AF%20ixxxxxw.cf%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%21,%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90Freenom%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%20%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E2%80%9CContinue%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E2%80%9CReview%20%26%20Checkout%E2%80%9D%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%20...%204%20%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86Freenom%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%20">使用freenom注册域名</a>（可能需用<a href="https://www.kwink.ml/posts/6410/">梯子</a>）</li><li>不用看CloudFlare配置</li></ul><h4 id="1-2解析DNS记录"><a href="#1-2解析DNS记录" class="headerlink" title="1.2解析DNS记录"></a>1.2解析DNS记录</h4><h5 id="1-2-1DNS转发"><a href="#1-2-1DNS转发" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1DNS转发"></a>1.2.1DNS转发</h5><h6 id="注册并登录CloudNS"><a href="#注册并登录CloudNS" class="headerlink" title="注册并登录CloudNS"></a>注册并登录<a href="https://www.cloudns.net/">CloudNS</a></h6><h6 id="创建域"><a href="#创建域" class="headerlink" title="创建域"></a>创建域</h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zO8DOI.png" alt="image-20221220212317974"></p><h6 id="输入之前注册的域名"><a href="#输入之前注册的域名" class="headerlink" title="输入之前注册的域名"></a>输入之前注册的域名</h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zO8Rfg.png" alt="image-20221220213609614"></p><h6 id="查看并复制图中标识位置"><a href="#查看并复制图中标识位置" class="headerlink" title="查看并复制图中标识位置"></a>查看并复制图中标识位置</h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOGQN8.png" alt="image-20221220213858840"></p><h6 id="转到并登录freenom"><a href="#转到并登录freenom" class="headerlink" title="转到并登录freenom"></a>转到并登录<a href="https://my.freenom.com/">freenom</a></h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOGMAf.png" alt="image-20221220214052761"></p><h6 id="域名配置DNS转发"><a href="#域名配置DNS转发" class="headerlink" title="域名配置DNS转发"></a>域名配置DNS转发</h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOGNBq.png" alt="image-20221220214521206"></p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOGJjs.png" alt="image-20221220214551380"></p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOGtun.png" alt="image-20221220214635775"></p><p>转到Cloudns域名管理界面，进行DNS验证</p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOYVeI.png" alt="image-20221220221008082"></p><h5 id="1-2-2域名绑定"><a href="#1-2-2域名绑定" class="headerlink" title="1.2.2域名绑定"></a>1.2.2域名绑定</h5><h6 id="返回github库-自定义域名"><a href="#返回github库-自定义域名" class="headerlink" title="返回github库,自定义域名"></a>返回github库,自定义域名</h6><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOYAOA.png" alt="image-20221220222100435"></p><p>根据<a href="https://docs.github.com/en/pages/configuring-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site/verifying-your-custom-domain-for-github-pages">Github提示</a>转到CloudNS域管理面板,添加DNS验证</p><p>然后就可以用域名访问你的网站了</p><h2 id="2-域名HTTP配置"><a href="#2-域名HTTP配置" class="headerlink" title="2.域名HTTP配置"></a>2.域名HTTP配置</h2><p>配置自己的域名后，需要我们手动开启 HTTPS。打开博客所在 GitHub 仓库，Settings -&gt; 下拉找到 GitHub Pages -&gt; 勾选 Enforce HTTPS。</p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/20/zOYkyd.png" alt="image-20221220224623575"></p><p>HTTPS 证书部署成功需要一定时间，等大概几分钟再访问域名，就可以看到域名前面的小绿锁了，HTTPS 配置完成！</p><p>——-Hexo+Github搭建网站系列——-</p><p><a href="https://www.kwink.ml/posts/d760/">Hexo+Github搭建网站系列：基础教程（一）</a></p><p><a href="https://www.kwink.ml/posts/990b/">Hexo+Github搭建网站系列：基础教程（二）</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
